{"tid":2452561,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[再招新血] 無錯，TG天秤谷係再招新人","createTime":"2021-03-19T02:15:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T11:40:37.000Z","uid":98151,"like":1,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e03af65104768bc04fb23518c263a6d3fa73169e","tid":2452561,"uid":98151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T02:15:17.000Z","msg":"我地天秤谷呢個大家庭唔經唔覺都差唔多一週年<br />\n大家都經歷左好多食飯、飲酒、開P、生日聚、燒野食、抱石......多不勝數活動<br />\n黎緊想再招新血入我地大家庭，同我地度一週年谷慶外<br />\n仲要繼續搞好多唔同類型活動<br />\n等大家識返更多同自己同一星座朋友仔外<br />\n仲可以比大家出多D活動，動一動身體，繼續咁健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n厹、收兵、騷擾人就必踢之外，基本無乜太多限制<br />\n有興趣既天秤朋友仔，禁入以下channel填好表格後，admin好快會搵你入谷，同大家聚一聚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/QcFW0uDg4dgRde8U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FQcFW0uDg4dgRde8U&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBSmo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=005d4d8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/QcFW0uDg4dgRde8U</a>"},{"pid":"ed871da13f030bf916773ef11360184f39b58a62","tid":2452561,"uid":98151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T05:11:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dc07abb883b4619317538b397d8be8c0299d7031","tid":2452561,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T05:12:54.000Z","msg":"有無獅子谷"},{"pid":"e374aabc26114fce315a40f5709b909a64f59bd0","tid":2452561,"uid":138138,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"dc07abb883b4619317538b397d8be8c0299d7031","tid":2452561,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T05:12:54.000Z","msg":"有無獅子谷"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T05:57:39.000Z","msg":"動物園有"},{"pid":"f180a8333beb946aaf00461efd5c9c64b6c11e54","tid":2452561,"uid":9392,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T06:22:39.000Z","msg":"不要說天秤仔天秤女 試著說on9仔on9女"},{"pid":"13aeff717396ffa06d8d7d6887200b574bf295dd","tid":